headline: TAKANOCK NAMES CRAIG MCKESSON CHIEF COMMERCIAL OFFICER TO ACCELERATE GROWTH STRATEGY
summary: Takanock, LLC, a provider of integrated power solutions for the digital infrastructure sector, today announced the appointment of Craig McKesson as chief commercial officer. McKesson joins the executive team as the company enters its next phase of execution following a $500 million capital commitment from ArcLight and DigitalBridge announced June 25.
